data.description: Spectacular Ranch home - Set on an stunning lot & detached garage. This one has it all, convenient location, and a fantastic price. The gourmet kitchen features beautiful cabinets with granite countertops, newer lighting, stainless steel appliances, dishwasher, stove, refrigerator and finished with custom backsplash. The entire home shines, an open Lay-Out, hardwood Kitchen Floor, vinyl siding, new exterior back deck, updated bathroom  Hot Water heating with newer baseboards. Perfect starter home or anyone that wants convenient living on a quiet dead end street, located close to shopping, and tucked away in a quiet neighborhood. One car detached is perfect for one car and lawn storage. Great finished enclosed front porch. BROKERS CALL TODAY !!! Please call for an appointment before walking around property. Lets show and sell - Unbelievable space for your BBQ parties, horseshoes, and other outdoor activates in the BACK YARD with a fenced in garden.
